789
00:53:05.891 --> 00:53:07.810
<i>Just trying to break
a little new ground.</i>

790
00:53:08.936 --> 00:53:10.187
<i>I dug deep.</i>

791
00:53:10.855 --> 00:53:12.439
<i>But I think
they have potential.</i>

792
00:53:18.028 --> 00:53:19.488
