00:53:22.657 --> 00:53:24.242
It's not just that.

795
00:53:24.243 --> 00:53:27.453
It's like he's channeling
something deeply personal

796
00:53:27.454 --> 00:53:28.956
and...

797
00:53:29.664 --> 00:53:32.251
quite frankly. you know. dark.

798
00:53:33.961 --> 00:53:37.506
These songs about somebody
who feels condemned.

799
