803
00:53:46.556 --> 00:53:49.558
The truth is I don't know
how to help him right now.

804
00:53:49.559 --> 00:53:50.895
I don't know
what to do with this.

805
00:53:53.605 --> 00:53:55.649
I think... I'm not gonna
say anything now.

806
00:53:56.358 --> 00:54:00.154
I'll see what the songs become
when we cut 'em with the band.

807
00:54:00.695 --> 00:54:02.531
