877
01:00:04.017 --> 01:00:05.518
<i>- with this thing.</i>
- Hey. Ma.

878
01:00:05.519 --> 01:00:06.477
<i>- I don't know.</i>
- Ma.

879
01:00:06.478 --> 01:00:08.271
- Hey.
<i>- Oh. honey. thank God.</i>

