01:07:35.677 --> 01:07:38.012
- We'll get it.
- Okay.

993
01:07:41.600 --> 01:07:42.601
Hey.

994
01:07:44.060 --> 01:07:45.311
We burned it down.

995
01:07:46.270 --> 01:07:47.897
Yeah. we burned it down.

996
01:09:06.893 --> 01:09:08.436
Yeah. how's Pop doing?

997
01:09:10.730 --> 01:09:12.647
<i>He's okay.</i>

998
01:09:12.648 --> 01:09:14.483
<i>He's sleeping right now.</i>

999
01:09:15.234 --> 01:09:16.235
<i>You know.</i>

1000
01:09:17.070 --> 01:09:18.779
<i>Honey. some days
are harder than others.</i>

1001
01:09:18.780 --> 01:09:20.448
<i>but we're just fine.</i>

1002
01:09:22.450 --> 01:09:23.534
Tell him I say hello.

1003
01:09:25.286 --> 01:09:26.870
<i>Oh. I sure will.</i>

1004
01:09:26.871 --> 01:09:29.332
<i>He always perks up
when he hears from you.</i>

1005
01:09:34.420 --> 01:09:37.005
Okay. Good night.

1006
01:09:37.006 --> 01:09:38.091
<i>Good night. sweetheart.</i>

1007
01:09:46.933 --> 01:09:53.022
<i>♪ From the town
Of Lincoln. Nebraska ♪</i>

1008
01:09:54.190 --> 01:10:00.822
<i>♪ With a sawed-off .410
On my lap ♪</i>

1009
01:10:02.490 --> 01:10:06.034
<i>♪ Through the badlands
Of Wyoming ♪</i>

1010
01:10:06.035 --> 01:10:07.328
No. it's all wrong.

1011
01:10:09.413 --> 01:10:12.458
I mean. the synth. mandolin.
electric guitar.

1012
01:10:13.292 --> 01:10:15.794
We're losing everything
I like about the demo.

1013
01:10:15.795 --> 01:10:17.838
It's getting buried
under these layers.

1014
01:10:17.839 --> 01:10:20.590
You know. I mean. this.
this has something. all right?

1015
01:10:20.591 --> 01:10:23.260
It's got the atmosphere. rawness.

1016
01:10:23.261 --> 01:10:25.596
It's got the right kinda echo.
and this just doesn't have it.

1017
01:10:26.472 --> 01:10:28.390
The band's overpowering
the material.

1018
01:10:28.391 --> 01:10:30.893
and we're losing
what makes it special to me.

1019
01:10:30.894 --> 01:10:32.394
I think
we gotta strip it back.

1020
01:10:32.395 --> 01:10:34.187
- Okay. but...
- Just let it breathe. right?

1021
01:10:34.188 --> 01:10:36.983
Let's move on. Right.

1022
01:10:38.109 --> 01:10:40.110
We got something
great yesterday.

1023
01:10:40.111 --> 01:10:41.487
Really powerful.

1024
01:10:42.989 --> 01:10:45.532
We just. you know.
we didn't get "Nebraska."

1025
01:10:45.533 --> 01:10:46.950
but we'll get there.

1026
01:10:46.951 --> 01:10:48.076
- Yeah.
- Okay?

1027
01:10:48.077 --> 01:10:50.789
We just-- We keep at it
like we always do.

1028
01:10:51.873 --> 01:10:52.874
Keep going.

1029
01:10:53.624 --> 01:10:54.793
Stay in the saddle.

1030
01:10:56.920 --> 01:10:58.295
You know.
maybe we give it a shot

1031
01:10:58.296 --> 01:11:01.215
with just you on acoustic.
Roy on piano.

1032
01:11:15.063 --> 01:11:17.355
I can't. Jon.

1033
01:11:17.356 --> 01:11:19.024
No. I can't...
I can't even listen to it.

1034
01:11:19.025 --> 01:11:20.568
It just makes me nauseous.

1035
01:11:33.206 --> 01:11:34.998
It's a process.

1036
01:11:34.999 --> 01:11:37.209
All right? We're getting a lot
of what we're after.

1037
01:11:37.210 --> 01:11:38.919
Maybe not everything.
but a lot.

1038
01:11:38.920 --> 01:11:40.170
I know. Jon. I know.

1039
01:11:40.171 --> 01:11:41.796
I know
we got good stuff. right?

1040
01:11:41.797 --> 01:11:44.799
But it's these songs.
"Nebraska." "Mansion"...

1041
01:11:44.800 --> 01:11:46.844
What they're doing with
"Atlantic City." it's just...

1042
01:11:46.845 --> 01:11:48.762
It's not working. Right?

1043
01:11:49.931 --> 01:11:52.475
And these songs. you know.
they matter to me.

1044
01:11:55.603 --> 01:11:56.645
Okay. hear me out.

1045
01:11:58.106 --> 01:11:59.565
Just hear me out.

1046
01:12:01.192 --> 01:12:03.527
Let's... Let's put that tape
aside for now.

1047
01:12:04.695 --> 01:12:06.030
Okay? We revisit it.

1048
01:12:07.115 --> 01:12:09.117
It ain't going anywhere
and neither are we.

1049
01:12:10.618 --> 01:12:12.494
We've got an incredible
take on "Cover Me"

1050
01:12:12.495 --> 01:12:14.580
which. thankfully. we didn't
give to Donna Summer.

1051
01:12:15.539 --> 01:12:18.376
We have "Glory Days."
"I'm Goin' Down."

1052
01:12:19.085 --> 01:12:20.628
and a knockout "I'm on Fire."

1053
01:12:22.171 --> 01:12:24.132
And don't forget.
we've got "Born in the U.S.A."

1054
01:12:27.093 --> 01:12:28.176
Did I tell you
what Iovine said

1055
01:12:28.177 --> 01:12:29.345
about "Born in the U.S.A."?

1056
01:12:30.638 --> 01:12:31.639
He was blown away.

1057
01:12:32.640 --> 01:12:34.099
Blown away.
He said the album's done.

1058
01:12:34.100 --> 01:12:35.433
That it could be
"Born in the U.S.A."

1059
01:12:35.434 --> 01:12:37.020
and ten other tracks.
and nobody would care.

1060
01:12:37.937 --> 01:12:40.106
He said with that song
leading. nothing else matters.

1061
01:12:41.524 --> 01:12:43.025
At this rate.

1062
01:12:43.026 --> 01:12:45.027
we'll have an album
mixed and mastered in no time.

1063
01:12:45.028 --> 01:12:46.320
Maybe even a month.

1064
01:12:46.988 --> 01:12:48.364
That's a record for us.

1065
01:12:49.490 --> 01:12:52.868
And this stuff. you know.
it's an evolution. Bruce.

1066
01:12:59.292 --> 01:13:02.295
<i>♪ My name is Joe Roberts ♪</i>

1067
01:13:04.088 --> 01:13:06.839
<i>♪ I work for the state... ♪</i>

1068
01:13:06.840 --> 01:13:08.300
Okay. baby.
I think we gotta go.

1069
01:13:08.301 --> 01:13:11.387
<i>♪ I'm a sergeant
Out of Perrineville ♪</i>

1070
01:13:12.846 --> 01:13:15.934
<i>♪ Barracks number eight ♪</i>

1071
01:13:17.560 --> 01:13:20.980
<i>♪ I always done
An honest job ♪</i>

1072
01:13:22.023 --> 01:13:25.234
<i>♪ As honest as I could ♪</i>

1073
01:13:26.235 --> 01:13:27.485
<i>Hey. it's me.</i>

1074
01:13:27.486 --> 01:13:28.403
<i>Leave me a message.</i>

1075
01:13:28.404 --> 01:13:29.696
<i>♪ I got a brother
Named Franky ♪</i>

1076
01:13:29.697 --> 01:13:31.031
<i>Hey. Bruce.
Would you pick up?</i>

1077
01:13:31.032 --> 01:13:32.075
<i>♪ And Franky ain't no good ♪</i>

1078
01:13:34.618 --> 01:13:36.286
Where were you today?

1079
01:13:36.287 --> 01:13:39.081
<i>♪ Now ever
Since we was young kids ♪</i>

1080
01:13:39.082 --> 01:13:40.457
<i>Bruce. I know you're there.</i>

1081
01:13:40.458 --> 01:13:43.294
<i>♪ It's been
The same come down ♪</i>

1082
01:13:45.171 --> 01:13:48.257
<i>♪ I get a call
On the short-wave ♪</i>

1083
01:13:48.967 --> 01:13:53.221
<i>♪ Franky's in trouble
