1084
01:13:54.347 --> 01:13:57.225
<i>♪ Well. if it was
Any other man ♪</i>

1085
01:13:57.725 --> 01:13:59.060
That's it.

1086
01:13:59.643 --> 01:14:02.270
That's the sound. Jon.
I wanna get Batlan over here.

1087
01:14:02.271 --> 01:14:04.939
We transfer everything
directly from this tape.

1088
01:14:04.940 --> 01:14:08.319
All right? No... No changes.
No nothing. Exactly as it is.

1089
01:14:11.489 --> 01:14:12.490
All right?

1090
01:14:13.199 --> 01:14:14.199
Okay.

1091
01:14:14.200 --> 01:14:16.076
♪ ...<i>Franky laughin'
And drinkin' ♪</i>

1092
01:14:25.836 --> 01:14:27.046
We're really doing this?

1093
01:14:28.422 --> 01:14:29.506
I mean...

1094
01:14:29.507 --> 01:14:32.550
unless you want us all
to look for a new job.

1095
01:14:32.551 --> 01:14:34.303
yes. you're really doing it.

1096
01:14:56.200 --> 01:15:01.914
<i>♪ I can't say that I'm sorry ♪</i>

1097
01:15:03.374 --> 01:15:04.582
<i>♪ For the things... ♪</i>

1098
01:15:04.583 --> 01:15:06.209
Nah. it's not the same.

1099
01:15:06.210 --> 01:15:08.086
<i>♪ That we done... ♪</i>

1100
01:15:08.087 --> 01:15:09.338
It's not the same.

1101
01:15:10.048 --> 01:15:11.714
We're in one
of the best recording studios

1102
01:15:11.715 --> 01:15:12.924
