<i>♪ Hey. little girl
Is your daddy home? ♪</i>

1211
01:20:49.428 --> 01:20:52.264
<i>♪ Did he go away
And leave you all alone? ♪</i>

1212
01:20:53.932 --> 01:20:56.018
<i>♪ I got a bad desire ♪</i>

1213
01:20:57.936 --> 01:21:01.524
<i>♪ Oh. oh. oh. I'm on fire ♪</i>

1214
01:21:03.108 --> 01:21:05.568
<i>♪ Tell me now. baby
Is he good to you? ♪</i>

1215
01:21:05.569 --> 01:21:08.279
<i>♪ Can he do to you
The things that I do? ♪</i>

1216
01:21:08.280 --> 01:21:09.407
<i>♪ No. no ♪</i>

1217
01:21:10.157 --> 01:21:12.034
<i>♪ I can take you higher ♪</i>

1218
01:21:13.869 --> 01:21:17.790
<i>♪ Oh. oh. oh. I'm on fire ♪</i>

1219
01:21:39.728 --> 01:21:41.854
<i>♪ Sometimes it's like
